 and PWA
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Add three high-impact features to improve user experience:

**1. Real-Time Notification System**
- WebSocket-based notification service for instant updates
- Auto-check deadlines, invoices, and budget alerts every 5 minutes
- Notification center UI with unread badge
- Browser notifications support
- Toast popups for urgent notifications

**2. Dark Mode**
- Three modes: Light, Dark, System
- Persistent theme preferences in localStorage
- Smooth theme transitions
- Theme toggle in header
- Uses existing CSS variables from index.css

**3. Progressive Web App (PWA)**
- Installable on desktop and mobile
- Offline functionality with Service Worker
- Intelligent caching strategy
- App manifest with shortcuts
- Push notification support
- Auto-update mechanism

**Technical Details:**
- New endpoints: /api/notifications, /ws/notifications
- New components: NotificationCenter, ThemeToggle
- New hooks: use-notifications, use-theme
- Service Worker with cache strategies
- Updated CSP to allow WebSocket connections

All features are production-ready and fully integrated.

